> > > requesting IRQ during device start which happens frequently.
> > >
> > > Suggested-by: Laurent Pinchart <laurent.pinchart+renesas@ideasonboard.com>
> > > Signed-off-by: Biju Das <biju.das.jz@bp.renesas.com>
